{"tid":2122262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自私撚周圍傳播武肺","createTime":"2020-07-24T01:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T01:57:40.000Z","uid":153357,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"895211317036454bae66668eb6f90f8b33879e8b","tid":2122262,"uid":153357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T01:57:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhMRyZB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhMRyZB.png&h=d482f478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n正正常常香港人已經唔點出街<br />\n班自私撚係疫情底下仲要堅持返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n周圍播毒 好心政府唔禁足 公司唔WFH就自己辭職留係屋企啦 唔好咁自私為咗自己份人工就要香港市民陪葬 諗吓自己屋企人 諗吓醫護啦  <br />\n銅鑼灣醫生戴口罩都感染啦 憑咩覺得你去返工就唔會播毒 點解唔可以忍一忍疫情完咗再搵工？<br />\n就係你地呢啲返工撚 仲去返工 日日過百單 又俾藉口政府瀨香港市民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好意思自我感覺良好批鬥人哋出街<br />\n屌 你估武肺識得認你係返工撚就唔感染你呀？"}]}